Mushroom Burger

25 min
$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten (if not using gluten-free buns)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickEasySavoryComfort Food

Description

A savory, juicy mushroom burger packed with flavor, perfect for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • portobello mushrooms: 2 large
  • burger buns: 2
  • cheddar cheese: 2 slices
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
